track_notes: This is the trail from Cole Mountain - go back to the car via Cole summit to the Cole Mountain trailhead

Trail track starts at Cole assuming a doubleheader.   More switchbacks than the original track.  This is based on the actual hike.  The summit of Cole is at mile 0.27 - so deduct that from the hike distance
Hike the AT starting at the parking area of Hog Camp Gap, up and over Cole Mt. back down to Cowcamp gap and back up to Bald Knob

Track includes round trip to Cole Mtn, Bald Knob and back to start. Start at (37.75681, -79.21597). This trailhead is accessible by motor vehicle only during hunting season. Hike trail 3226 (not shown on most maps but in good condition) to AT at Cowcamp Gap to either or both summits.
